<h1>CARRIE</h1><h2 class="sub">Computational Ascertainment of Regulatory Relationships (Inferred from Expression)</h2>

<p>CARRIE takes two condition microarray data and applies promoter
analysis to infer the stimulated/repressed transcriptional regulatory network.</p>

<form method="post" action="../cgi-bin/index.cgi" enctype="multipart/form-data">

<h3>1. Upload Array Data</h3>
<input type="radio" name="data_type" value="preprocessed" checked><a href="javascript:showPopup('preprocessed')"> Pre-Processed</a><br>
<input type="radio" name="data_type" value="unprocessed" ><a href="javascript:showPopup('unprocessed')"> Un-Processed</a><br>
<input type="file" name="array_file"  size="40" maxlength="150">

<h3>2. Choose Criteria for Significant Expression Change</h3>
<textarea name="fold_change" cols=5 rows=1>2</textarea><a href="javascript:showPopup('fold_change')"> Fold Change</a><br>
<textarea name="array_pvalue" cols=5 rows=1>0.01</textarea><a href="javascript:showPopup('array_pvalue')"> P-value</a><br>

<h3>3. Choose Matrix List</h3>
<select name="matrix_list">
